			School Closure and Related Health Information – updated 4/24/20			        </h1>
		
				<div class="post-meta clearfix">
			
									<span class="printonly">Categories: </span>
			<p class="meta_categories"><a href="http://www.bcreek.k12.mi.us/?cat=3" rel="category">All District</a>, <a href="http://www.bcreek.k12.mi.us/?cat=25" rel="category">Community</a>, <a href="http://www.bcreek.k12.mi.us/?cat=12" rel="category">Front Page News</a></p>
						
						            
                        			
